		<p class="lead">Discovering a damaged fence on your Stockton property can be stressful, especially when it affects your privacy, security, or curb appeal. Whether the damage resulted from severe weather, accidents, or normal wear and tear, knowing the right steps to take can save you time, money, and prevent further complications.</p>
		
